<p>
<h2>
	Research interests
</h2>
<span style="font-size:16px">
I am working at the intersection between machine learning, healthcare and bioinformatics, developing new machine learning methods to resolve the computational problems in biology and healthcare, especially the structured learning problems. <br>
My long-term goal is to improve the healthcare system, benefiting society directly by improving people's health and wellness. <br>
